EmailTemplate.subject: Reminder: Twilight Tour/St Andrew's Cathedral School 2 April 2014
EmailTemplate.textOnly:
Hello {!Contact.FirstName}, we are very excited at the wonderful response we have received to our Junior School Information Evening and Twilight Tour! Thank you for taking and distributing the invitiations at your Centre.
There a still a few spaces left if there are any families who wish to come along and it's not too late to book
Just a reminder that there is a supervised creche being provided on the evening for those who need it. Bookings can be made direct through me to rpedley@sacs.nsw.edu.au or by phone on 9286 9552.
Wishing you and the families of {!Account.Name} a safe and happy Easter.
Regards
Robyn
